verbose_text: The results revealed that, siRNA targeting of HOXA5 in Jurkat cells after 24 h decreased the expression of HOXA5 protein, pRNAT-GFP-Neo-HOXA5A (0.64 +/-0.15), pRNAT-GFP-Neo-HOXA5B (0.41 +/-0.06), pRNAT-GFP-Neo-HOXA5C (0.17 +/-0.05), negative control group (0.73 +/-0.12), and the blank control group (0.73 +/-0.13) (XREF_FIG).
